{"tid":461932,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益去李健學車好定香港駕駛學院好","createTime":"2017-11-08T05:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T03:25:54.000Z","uid":54817,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"be20c0f00f71db9d20e858b8c2e51c6cfab60b3b","tid":461932,"uid":54817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T05:56:37.000Z","msg":"邊個會好d？"},{"pid":"8ced90f77d2b67c053bdd0ee1d120283ece07358","tid":461932,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:06:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1862472acd08f2a7d79eb9320917b48a46ee27c0","tid":461932,"uid":42362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"駕駛學院考既路線同其他非駕駛學院既人唔同<br />\n<br />\n李健=正常路線<br />\n<br />\n所以駕駛學院先敢收咁貴"},{"pid":"4aed757443a5770f06739eed9e13646b1f08c9f9","tid":461932,"uid":71960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:09:02.000Z","msg":"你見過李健未呀"},{"pid":"744cbdfdc9af772cb3a264360052320b65995daf","tid":461932,"uid":42362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:12:10.000Z","msg":"仲有街場只可以揀2個地區<br />\n- 香港<br />\n- 九龍/新界<br />\n<br />\n試場係random, 你重考都係random<br />\n<br />\n相反你去駕院, 如果你揀左元朗駕駛學院就一定係元朗考, 重考都係<br />\n<br />\n邊個易D好明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過就貴好多<br />\n<br />\n同埋你都預左駕院本身D堂唔夠, 你要俾錢出去搵師傅補鐘/係駕院補鐘<br />\n<br />\n至於有人話駕院學完之後都唔識揸車就算夠數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為你考完車都係要慢慢操先會熟<br />\n<br />\n雖然我就唔係去駕院, 因為係窮撚"},{"pid":"95099ab8e542f334eb56ae857600026a5b31eccb","tid":461932,"uid":10971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:46:38.000Z","msg":"李健平 快 難d<br />\n駕院自己場 感覺上易d 但排期耐同貴"},{"pid":"c4658c8b04f0689b944534d15746dbc6a63395b3","tid":461932,"uid":10133,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T10:16:43.000Z","msg":"唔撚學最好"},{"pid":"5515a7be3175d25f2d6a7260bfbea0e7da171329","tid":461932,"uid":113648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:25:54.000Z","msg":"一take pass左跑馬地試場"}]}